{"data":[{"date":"07:26 19/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Colombia-vs-Nhat.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Tottenham Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 minh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 18/6.</h2><h2>Son Heung-min nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u 18/6. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1 chi\u1ec1u qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, khi m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi v\u1ec1 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i \u1edf Tottenham, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;Khi t\u00f4i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u1edf Tottenham&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23.6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Rostov Arena (Rostov). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"335","checkdouble":"188891"},{"date":"07:31 19/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/sao-ha-noi-doi-mat-an-treo-gio-sau-tran-thua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Oseni hay trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Dao-Duy-Khanh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o Nam \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y x\u1ea5u tr\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-5 chung cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ecb ng\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 75, trong l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn 4-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o c\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Da Sylva trong l\u00fac ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i k\u00edn c\u1ee7a Duy Kh\u00e1nh d\u0129 nhi\u00ean qua m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Thu\u1eadn&nbsp;song h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 98 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1eedi ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, VFF l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas Tardin, trong khi Oseni c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn c\u0169ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u1ea1m M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a&nbsp;SLNA.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?</span><br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League, b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n quanh tr\u1eadn thua...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Antenna-Regular, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"334","checkdouble":"188892"},{"date":"07:52 19/06","title":"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i t\u1edbi sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y &lsquo;nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rsquo; v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, BHL \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Italia ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn play-off gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-DT-Han-Quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 huy b\u1edfi &lsquo;th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh&rsquo; Andreas Granqvist n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, &lsquo;c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Viking&rsquo; thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. H\u1ecd b\u00edt ch\u1eb7t m\u1ecdi l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Olsen v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c mi\u1ebfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Ph\u00fat 20, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb B\u1eafc \u00c2u n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Marcus Berg kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang ch\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-woo ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ee9u thua. Sau th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ibrahimovic, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1, tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Mexico, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>VAR l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i &lsquo;nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk&rsquo;<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video VAR (video assistant referee) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FIFA mang t\u1edbi k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 xem l\u1ea1i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p &ndash; \u00dac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO 2016. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, VAR l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Kim chi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &lsquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rsquo; ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/11_QEFD.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3&nbsp;VAR</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ed5 ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 63 khi Min Woo va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Claesson trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Aguilar Joel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en ng\u01b0\u1eddi El Salvador \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a VAR. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau khi xem r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 b\u0103ng quay ch\u1eadm, \u00f4ng Aguilar Joel \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m\u00e9t, &quot;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&quot; Granqvist \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-woo, ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 VAR th\u00ec h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Shin Tae-yong r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng - playmaker khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. V\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c trung phong cao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u00ecm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ea7u. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, t\u01b0 duy gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1_YPEA.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng 'g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3' Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady,khi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u00ec H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. D\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Son Heung-min, Ki Sung Yong, Lee Chung Yong hay Ji Dong Won nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, HLV Shin Tae-yong \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5t tay khi tung ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&rsquo; Lee Seung-woo v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 20 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-c469-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup </span>n\u0103m nay, khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188854.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/5-diem-nhan-Thuy-Dien-vs-Han-Quoc-bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188854.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m c\u1ee7a Granqvist. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188857.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188857.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"333","checkdouble":"188894"},{"date":"08:11 19/06","title":"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Tottenham Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 minh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 18/6.</h2><h2>Son Heung-min nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u 18/6. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1 chi\u1ec1u qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, khi m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi v\u1ec1 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i \u1edf Tottenham, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;Khi t\u00f4i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u1edf Tottenham&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23.6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Rostov Arena (Rostov). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"332","checkdouble":"188895"},{"date":"08:31 19/06","title":"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/13/hlv-dt-nga-tu-tin-doi-pho-voi-ai-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u then ch\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u then ch\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u00f3 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp b\u1edfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh ba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Uruguay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/HLV-DT-Nga-tu-tin-doi-pho-voi-Ai-Cap-cua-Mohamed-Salah-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3&nbsp;v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebd trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u qua 18/6, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, \u00f4ng Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ri\u00eang c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u0110T Nga t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp. V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Salah, HLV tuy\u1ec3n Nga, Cherchesov tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi: ''T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra v\u1ec1, \u00f4ng Cherchesov c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 54 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u0110T Nga, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Nga \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa \u0110T Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6, theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn. K\u00ednh m\u1eddi qu\u00fd v\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo-alan-dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-421-188749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/Dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo,-Alan-Dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo-alan-dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-421-188749.html\">\u0110T Nga nh\u1eadn hung tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Sky Sports, g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0110T Nga, Alan Dzagoev s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay: Salah bu\u1ed3n, Suarez n\u00e0o c\u00f3 vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi Salah bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00e0o ph\u00fat...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"331","checkdouble":"188896"},{"date":"08:18 19/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Senegal (22h ng\u00e0y 19/6): \u0110\u1ea1i ph\u00e1o so t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-ba-lan-vs-senegal-22h-ngay-196-dai-phao-so-tai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Sadio Mane. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1ng xem gi\u1eefa hai tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Lewandowski v\u00e0 Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Senegal (22h ng\u00e0y 196) \u0110\u1ea1i ph\u00e1o so t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Senegal (22h ng\u00e0y 196) \u0110\u1ea1i ph\u00e1o so t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Ba-Lan-vs-Senegal.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Senegal (b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba Lan \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u00e0i n\u0103ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Lewandowski. V\u00e0 Senegal th\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean l\u00e0 Sadio Mane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup. Anh ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Lewandowski c\u00f2n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 16 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngu\u1ed3n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lewandowski th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Ba Lan khi n\u00f3 chi\u1ebfm h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Lewandowski c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf Bundesliga v\u1edbi 29 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. T\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 41 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i Ba Lan khi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdng s\u00fang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Mane \u0111\u00e3 ghi 20 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Liverpool, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 10 b\u00e0n \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Mane ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m duy nh\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane Lewandowski\" title=\"Mane Lewandowski\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/081202-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecd t\u00e0i Lewandowski \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-h-world-cup-2018-ai-theo-buoc-colombia-469-187911.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018</span>, HLV Aliou Cisse c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Senegal: &ldquo;Sadio Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 d\u00f9 cho r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Mane v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n nh\u01b0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Olympic 2012.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t v\u00f4 nh\u1ecb v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111o\u00e1n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n hay m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tong hop: Ba Lan 4-0 Lithuania (Giao huu quoc te)\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 4-0 Lithuania (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/tong-hop-ba-lan-40-lithuania-giao-huu-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ba Lan c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tuy hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm gi\u1eef ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn hay qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba Lan c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i cho NHM c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tuy kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ba Lan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu m\u00ecnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00f3n \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n Senegal th\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Mane. Trung v\u1ec7 Koulibaly \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Napoli nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho Senegal. Do v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ba Lan gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u1eefa Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u1edf World Cup (th\u1eafng 1 h\u00f2a 2). 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 thua 6/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Ba Lan gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf World Cup l\u00e0 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1986</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ba Lan kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 5 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi 16 b\u00e0n. Anh ghi 57% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ba Lan. C\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ba Lan ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 Kamil Grosicki</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (th\u1eafng 1 h\u00f2a 2) trong l\u1ea7n tham gia v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Diafra Sakho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Senegal ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup th\u1ee9 3 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u Phi. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n Sadio Mane \u1edf c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 (3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Ba Lan vs Senegal\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ba Lan vs Senegal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Ba-Lan-vs-Senegal-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ba Lan vs Senegal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-ba-lan-tai-world-cup-2018-phai-cho-lewandowski-469-187993.html\">\u0110T Ba Lan t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-senegal-tai-world-cup-2018-hy-vong-vao-ky-tich-469-188074.html\">\u0110T Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"330","checkdouble":"188897"},{"date":"08:49 19/06","title":"Kyle Walker: \"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia t\u1ef1 lao v\u00e0o c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/kyle-walker-cau-thu-thuy-si-tu-lao-vao-cui-cho-cua-toi.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t penalty c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 Tunisia v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi Harry Kane m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb s\u1edbm. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho Tunisia h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Walker v\u1edbi Fakhreddine Ben Youssef.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ferjani Sassi sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Tunisia. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi. Nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do-421-188883.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng</span> v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kyle Walker th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia t\u1ef1 lao v\u00e0o c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia t\u1ef1 lao v\u00e0o c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/kyle-walker-cau-thu-thuy-si-tu-lao-vao-cui-cho-cua-toi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Kyle Walker kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u1ede Premier League, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf World Cup, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u1ea1i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t. Trippier \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi t\u00f4i b\u1ecf qua t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng im. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia \u0111\u00e2m s\u1ea7m v\u00e0o tay t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1eeba c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u00e0 chung t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Panama, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Tunisia 1-2 Anh: Harry Kane! X\u1ee9ng danh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\">Gareth Southgate: Ngo\u00e0i Kane, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"329","checkdouble":"188898"},{"date":"08:49 19/06","title":"\u0110T Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef v\u1ec1 Neymar sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/dt-brazil-nhan-tin-du-ve-neymar-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica, \u0110T Brazil \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar sau nh\u1eefng va ch\u1ea1m \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Brazil \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 r\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb d\u00e3y n\u00fai Alps h\u00f9ng v\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec7u nh\u1ea3y Samba tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ea1c nh\u1ecbp, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/dt-brazil-nhan-tin-du-ve-neymar-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Selecao, Neymar c\u0169ng l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1ea5t. Kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n sau nh\u1eefng pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup t\u00ednh t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn England th\u1eafng Tunisia 2-0 t\u1ea1i France 98<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Neymar t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn BHL Brazil l\u1eabn HLV Tite h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c lo ng\u1ea1i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m 18/6 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi Costa Rica.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Neymar, Brazil c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 g\u1ed3m Marcelo, Gabriel Jesus v\u00e0 Thiago Silva. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Neymar, c\u1ea3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang h\u00f4m 18/6.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018-466-188838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018-466-188838.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Brazil ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn Selecao b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy-421-188829.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy-421-188829.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<em>Highlight: Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"328","checkdouble":"188899"},{"date":"03:10 19/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tunisia 1-2 Anh (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 2-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+1.</h2>Link xem: <span href=\"http://worldcup.vtv.vn/tin-tuc-app-the-thao/xem-truc-tiep-fifa-world-cup-2018-dt-tunisia-dt-anh-20180619001128975.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://worldcup.vtv.vn/tin-tuc-app-the-thao/xem-truc-tiep-fifa-world-cup-2018-dt-tunisia-dt-anh-20180619001128975.htm</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br />\r\nAnh: Pickford; Walker, Stones, Maguire; Trippier, Young, Henderson, Alli (Loftus-Cheek 80'), Lingard (Dier 90'+2), Sterling (Rashford 68'), Kane<br />\r\nTunisia: Hassen (Ben Mustapha 15'), Bronn, Ben Youssef, Meriah, Maaloul, Skhiri, Sassi (Ben Amor 73'), Sliti, Khazri (Khalifa 85'), Badri, Ben Youssef<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"327","checkdouble":"188877"},{"date":"04:02 19/06","title":"HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \u201cC\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/pv-gareth-southgate-sau-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp n\u1ed7i ni\u1ec1m ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Tunisia 1-2 Anh ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua hai k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef1a trung c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn Tam S\u01b0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, xen gi\u1eefa b\u1edfi qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a Tunisia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea3o qu\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thanh tho\u00e1t nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u1eafc Phi, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/pv-gareth-southgate-sau-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh - Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu sao, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/anh-vs-tunisia-bang-g-463-188846.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tunisia 1-2 Anh</span>. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i: \u201cNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay th\u01b0\u1eddng ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n, v\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i tin ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn trong hi\u1ec7p hai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng duy tr\u00ec nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d \u2013 HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G do k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 so v\u1edbi B\u1ec9. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd ngh\u00eanh \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n binh Panama v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Tunisia 1-2 Anh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tunisia 1-2 Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Thong-so-Anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tunisia 1-2 Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"326","checkdouble":"188879"},{"date":"03:46 19/06","title":"Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n kh\u1ee7ng, fan M.U l\u1ea1i l\u00f4i\u2026 Morata ra d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKane r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Harry Kane s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng sai l\u1ea7m ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9ng c\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb chia \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0ng do c\u00f4ng Harry Kane m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e1ng ra to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 World Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y\" title=\"Kane vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui v\u1ebb l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0i qu\u1ea3 penalty, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Tunisia. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n khi chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 Jordan Henderson c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, anh cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G, Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\">Gareth Southgate: Ngo\u00e0i Kane, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i</span><br>\r\nGareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-noi-bat-tran-anh-21-tunisia-421-188876.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Ket-qua-Tunisia-vs-Anh-tran-dau-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-noi-bat-tran-anh-21-tunisia-421-188876.html\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea trong tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tunisia 1-2 Anh (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 2-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"325","checkdouble":"188880"},{"date":"04:26 19/06","title":"Th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama ch\u1ec9 \"nh\u0103m nhe\" ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/thang-thuyet-phuc-courtois-chi-trich-panama-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m, v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 r\u1eafn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCourtois kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Panama<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi 3 pha ghi b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Panama kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Courtois t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Panama, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hung d\u1eef. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Panama li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama ch\u1ec9 nh\u0103m nhe ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama ch\u1ec9 nh\u0103m nhe ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/thang-thuyet-phuc-courtois-chi-trich-panama-choi-xau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 cho d\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ngay. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cB\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u00f3 th\u00f4i\u201d \u2013 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft nhau trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mong \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama-421-188873.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama-421-188873.html\">Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00ednh nh\u00e2n v\u0103n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama</span><br>\r\nRomelu Lukaku n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Panama, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi anh l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Mertens v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"324","checkdouble":"188881"},{"date":"04:30 19/06","title":"Gareth Southgate: \"Ngo\u00e0i Kane, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Harry Kane.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Southgate kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong h\u01a1n 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 18 l\u1ea7n, 8 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Tunisia d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 6 l\u1ea7n, ch\u1ec9 1 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tunisia-vs-anh-bang-g-421-188855.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Tunisia vs Anh </span>gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHarry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Anh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Kane d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Duy nh\u1ea5t Kane l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n&nbsp;l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Southgate c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" title=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gareth Southgate khen ng\u1ee3i&nbsp;</span>Harry Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 1-1 v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, song t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng Anh s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i linh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Tunisia 1-2 Anh: Harry Kane! X\u1ee9ng danh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\nHarry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Harry Kane, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"323","checkdouble":"188882"},{"date":"04:57 19/06","title":"L\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i Tam S\u01b0, Harry Kane ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKane r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Harry Kane s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng sai l\u1ea7m ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9ng c\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb chia \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0ng do c\u00f4ng Harry Kane m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e1ng ra to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 World Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y\" title=\"Kane vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui v\u1ebb l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0i qu\u1ea3 penalty, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Tunisia. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n khi chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 Jordan Henderson c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, anh cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G, Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\">Gareth Southgate: Ngo\u00e0i Kane, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i</span><br>\r\nGareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-noi-bat-tran-anh-21-tunisia-421-188876.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Ket-qua-Tunisia-vs-Anh-tran-dau-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-noi-bat-tran-anh-21-tunisia-421-188876.html\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u1eadn Tunisia 1-2 Anh</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea trong tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tunisia 1-2 Anh (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 2-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"322","checkdouble":"188883"},{"date":"04:55 19/06","title":"Hazard: \"Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm m\u1edbi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Eden Hazard c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f2n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ea1i London, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Nh\u1edd Chelsea, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u HLV Conte c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup\" title=\"Hazard vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ng\u00e0y mai, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. \u1ede l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu CLB c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i, m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, trong \u0111\u00f3 Hazard g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0110T n\u00e0o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Thong-so-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JP